1
00:01:08,319 --> 00:01:10,319
I had a long nightmare.

2
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:13,400
I dreamed that

3
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:16,040
I was in a vacuum.

4
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:18,480
And someone was talking to me.

5
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:32,760
Who is she?

6
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,519
My Lady?

7
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,760
You two look the same.

8
00:01:44,359 --> 00:01:46,120
I even suspected that you were Ms. Li,

9
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,560
pretending to lose your memory in front of My Lord.

10
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:49,359
In my previous life,

11
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,799
I was your master.

12
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,120
Yeah.

13
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,799
They say a dog can remember

14
00:01:57,879 --> 00:01:59,079
who fed it for three days.

15
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:00,840
You're just an ungrateful wolf.

16
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,680
If I hadn't remembered,

17
00:02:02,799 --> 00:02:04,200
you wouldn't have recognized me at all.

18
00:02:04,719 --> 00:02:06,000
You made me suffer so much.

19
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,079
Recognize?

20
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:08,759
Do you still dream of

21
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,400
taming me for all eternity?

22
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,800
Now I know

23
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,039
why we have brands.

24
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,439
It means

25
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:18,719
you

26
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,199
are my dog.

27
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:23,639
Don't even think about it.

28
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,319
Then I'll summon Li Feiyuan

29
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:27,800
to punish you herself.

30
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:28,479
You...

31
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:31,879
Bro.

32
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:33,120
Miss Jiang.

33
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:35,240
Let's calm down first.

34
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:37,120
Let's figure out

35
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,479
what's going on.

36
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,360
In quantum mechanics,

37
00:02:41,599 --> 00:02:42,599
all information

38
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:44,680
that has ever existed in the universe

39
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:47,080
will be stored in a flowing place

40
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:49,759
that permeates the entire universe,

41
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,039
called the zero-point field.

42
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:53,319
When the dead leave,

43
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:58,879
their memories

44
00:02:59,719 --> 00:03:00,560
are preserved.

45
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,560
When the later generations come into contact with it,

46
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:08,199
they will have the memories of the past,

47
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:10,280
even the memories of their past lives.

48
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:13,560
No wonder there's always a voice

49
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,080
talking to me in my head,

50
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,240
scaring me,

51
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,360
yet making me feel close.

52
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,199
What does she say to you?

53
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,080
That's between us.

54
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,879
Why tell you?

55
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,560
Those past ties

56
00:03:40,479 --> 00:03:42,159
are all about Li Feiyuan.

57
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:47,120
If extra memories trouble you,

58
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:48,759
you can choose to forget.

59
00:03:51,039 --> 00:03:52,039
I just feel

60
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,719
this is all incredible.

61
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,400
I came here to find my identity,

62
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,560
but I found my past life instead.

63
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,400
To find your identity?

64
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:07,479
I was abandoned on the beach as a child,

65
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,560
so I often have hallucinations of drowning.

66
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,159
My adoptive uncle told me

67
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,439
that it was just a nightmare.

68
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:15,800
My brother also...

69
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,000
Brother,

70
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:23,560
are you leaving?

71
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,600
I've been away from home too long.

72
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,959
My family will be worried,

73
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,600
Especially my brother.

74
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,439
He just said he was outside now.

75
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:33,839
My phone is out of power.

76
00:04:34,079 --> 00:04:35,079
Can I borrow yours?

77
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,240
I don't have one.

78
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,720
We can communicate

79
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,279
by telepathy.

80
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:43,680
What?

81
00:04:44,199 --> 00:04:45,399
What do you usually do

82
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,199
when you're bored?

83
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:48,720
You don't even have WeChat?

84
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:54,399
How dare you question my authority?

85
00:04:57,759 --> 00:04:58,959
Pretend I didn't say anything.

86
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,319
Jiang Yue,

87
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,920
just a casual question.

88
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:22,040
Will you come back

89
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:23,839
after you leave?

90
00:05:32,959 --> 00:05:33,839
I mean,

91
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:35,720
your research

92
00:05:35,759 --> 00:05:36,759
isn't finished, right?

93
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,879
When you're not angry,

94
00:05:42,759 --> 00:05:43,920
you're actually quite nice.

95
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:47,519
No, I...

96
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,040
I'm nice?

97
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,439
Nonsense.

98
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:55,040
At least you're better than when we first met.

99
00:05:55,839 --> 00:05:57,560
When you first caught me,

100
00:05:59,519 --> 00:06:01,399
you treated me like I killed you in another life.

101
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:11,480
Go pack your things.

102
00:06:11,839 --> 00:06:12,600
I'll take you out.

103
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:16,480
I knew it wouldn't last long.

104
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,160
I think the master is sad.

105
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,680
The master has lived for more than a thousand years.

106
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,319
He's seen everything.

107
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,000
This is nothing.

108
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:31,519
He won't be sad.

109
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,079
Old Wang, what are you doing?

110
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,480
I'm fighting against time.

111
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:43,680
You can live for thousands of years,

112
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:44,920
but I can only live for hundreds of years.

113
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,879
I have to take good care of myself.

114
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:50,079
What do you think of this?

115
00:06:52,879 --> 00:06:54,319
That's why you are wolves.

116
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,120
Too naive.

117
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,439
Stubborn.

118
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,759
In my opinion,

119
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:01,480
I want Miss Jiang

120
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,959
and Li Feiyuan

121
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,759
I want them both.

122
00:07:23,399 --> 00:07:24,040
Is he your brother?

123
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:24,920
Yeah.

124
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,079
Brother?

125
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,839
You are Lu Zhiyu?

126
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:32,519
Did Qin Yeren tell you that?

127
00:07:34,879 --> 00:07:36,000
Don't lie to me.

128
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:39,480
The smell of tobacco and fish on you

129
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,680
is as disgusting as his.

130
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,040
I have business dealings with Qin Yeren.

131
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:47,839
The Xie Group's business

132
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,279
spans the entire Pacific.

133
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,120
Maybe your place

134
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,319
will be acquired by me in the future.

135
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:57,240
Brother,

136
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:59,319
Qin Yeren is the bad guy.

137
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,759
He kidnapped me.

138
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:02,519
It was Lu Zhiyu who saved me.

139
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,199
I came here to travel,

140
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,319
and he's my local guide.

141
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:15,800
Yue,

142
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:17,560
don't hang out with this kind of person.

143
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,319
Let's go.

144
00:08:18,759 --> 00:08:19,240
Wait.

145
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,959
Miss Jiang hired me as her bodyguard.

146
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,759
Her journey isn't over,

147
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,319
and my job isn't finished either.

148
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:32,159
We can't separate.

149
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,039
Let's go.

150
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:34,759
Next stop.

151
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:36,320
Brother,

152
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,320
then you go ahead with your work.

153
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,519
Yue, we'll keep in touch.

154
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:56,919
Dad,

155
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,240
I've already met Qin Yeren.

156
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,840
He has conflicts with local gangs.

157
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:03,480
Don't worry,

158
00:09:03,679 --> 00:09:04,399
I'll handle it.

159
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,320
How are you planning to handle it?

160
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:08,759
Take down their base.

161
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,720
Chen,

162
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,600
you need to think more carefully.

163
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,360
If you help Qin Yeren,

164
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:15,039
it's like telling everyone

165
00:09:15,039 --> 00:09:17,519
that Xie Group is involved in illegal fishing.

166
00:09:17,759 --> 00:09:19,320
The land on Black Rock Island is good.

167
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,840
Buy it and build a factory.

168
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,600
Also,

169
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,639
bring Moon back as soon as possible.

170
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,840
You don't want her to know

171
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,759
what business you're in, do you?

172
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:34,360
[All is safe.]

173
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,480
[Only a fishing boat]

174
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,960
[was sneaking around the lighthouse.]

175
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,799
[It's been driven away by Li Si.]

176
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:41,200
The place where my mom and I were attacked

177
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:43,600
is connected to them.

178
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:44,759
After all these years,

179
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:47,159
Qin Yeren still hasn't given up.

180
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,480
So,

181
00:09:49,799 --> 00:09:50,919
Qin Yeren has been competing with you

182
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,080
for the lighthouse port.

183
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,159
What happened between you two before?

184
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:56,639
Qin Yeren used to be a fisherman,

185
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,679
making a fortune by smuggling seafood.

186
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:00,200
After I drove him away,

187
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:01,279
he never gave up.

188
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:02,799
He started recruiting thugs

189
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:05,159
and gradually became a gang boss.

190
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:09,399
Compared to Lu,

191
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,399
you are

192
00:10:12,919 --> 00:10:14,759
more valuable to me.

193
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,519
Let's work together

194
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,080
and give him a taste of his own medicine.

195
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:24,120
I'm having a hard time figuring out

196
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,200
which side you're on.

197
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,440
I've already explained.

198
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:30,720
Xie Chen is my adopted brother.

199
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:31,960
He's been good to me since childhood.

200
00:10:32,879 --> 00:10:34,799
The Xie Group's business has nothing to do with me.

201
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,159
He's not your biological brother.

202
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,559
Your focus is really...

203
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,120
Old Wang,

204
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:41,159
keep an eye on Xie.

205
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,039
and keep me updated.

206
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:43,919
Yes.

207
00:10:47,279 --> 00:10:48,320
From now on,

208
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:51,399
you need to stay by my side all the time.

209
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:54,759
You...

210
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:56,519
ordering me?

211
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,600
How dare you bite the hand

212
00:10:59,799 --> 00:11:00,759
that feeds you?

213
00:11:02,039 --> 00:11:02,759
Good dog.

214
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:03,639
Sit.

215
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,120
Go, go, go.

216
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:13,799
Go, go.

217
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:18,320
I'm warning you,

218
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,519
don't come near me.

219
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:26,240
You're no longer Li Feiyuan,

220
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,480
and you have no right to order me around.

221
00:11:28,879 --> 00:11:29,840
Watch your step.

222
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,679
You should be the one to watch your step.

223
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,440
What if

224
00:11:34,159 --> 00:11:35,679
I am Li Feiyuan?

225
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,320
Then I'll bite you to death.

226
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,120
Revenge.

227
00:11:47,879 --> 00:11:48,639
Wait for me.

228
00:11:56,519 --> 00:11:57,399
If it weren't for

229
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:00,440
Lu had been holding me back,

230
00:12:01,559 --> 00:12:03,200
she would have died hundreds of times.

231
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,399
Hundreds of times?

232
00:12:06,559 --> 00:12:07,320
What are you doing?

233
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:08,720
My lady,

234
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:10,720
my lady

235
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:11,559
wants to see you.

236
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:12,080
Why?

237
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:13,600
My lady is using some guys

238
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,120
as targets in the gym.

239
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,559
If you don't come...

240
00:12:21,399 --> 00:12:22,600
Xiaoya, stop it.

241
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:26,080
Look at these losers.

242
00:12:26,759 --> 00:12:27,879
None of them are good enough for me.

243
00:12:28,919 --> 00:12:29,960
You're looking for bodyguards,

244
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,279
not boyfriends.

245
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,279
I've already picked my boyfriend.

246
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,440
I want that man

247
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:36,000
I saw at the boxing match that day.

248
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:38,639
I've found out where he lives.

249
00:12:40,559 --> 00:12:41,240
Just wait.
